e logs/metrics only, not a surviving fix commit, so this looks like an automation handoff/preservation failure after multiple test-fix attempts.\n\nManual next steps:\n1. Reconstruct the attempted source changes from `human-intervention-logs/org.jline:jline-reader:4.0.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-04T03-07-14-815397Z.log`, especially the `FileNameCompleter` import change in `Jline_readerTest` and the `PipedInputStream`/`Ctrl-X` change in `LineReaderImplTest`.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.jline:jline-reader:4.0.0` and `./gradlew nativeTest -Pcoordinates=org.jline:jline-reader:4.0.0` to confirm the fix outside the automation loop.\n3. If native verification still fails, inspect metadata/resource registration for `META-INF/jline/providers/ffm` and `META-INF/jline/providers/jni`."}}
